00:09:30,100 --> 00:09:31,800
So, the original image is 6 by 6.

283
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,180
and after it scans through,

284
00:09:33,180 --> 00:09:34,300
without any special padding,

285
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:35,220
So, after scanning,

