00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:07,680
So, if our K is equal to three...

368
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:08,380
K is equal to three,

369
00:12:08,380 --> 00:12:12,630
So basically, it means a 3x3 convolutional kernel with P equal to one.

370
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:14,170
so we'll pad it with a一圈一 of zeros.

371
00:12:14,170 --> 00:12:15,430
And S equals one.

